尽管电子政务的开发和实施"花费了巨额资本"，有些人说只获得了平庸的表现。实验性的互联网政府的结果、效果很难衡量。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.economist.com/surveys/displaystory.cfm?STORY_ID=10638105 |title=The pros and cons of e-government |publisher=Economist |date=2008-02-14 |accessdate=2009-02-28 |archive-date=2009-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090519151620/http://www.economist.com/surveys/displaystory.cfm?story_id=10638105 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
